{"tid":1816494,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"繼續將文宣注入節日! 新一批揮春設計圖流出!","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T01:33:55.000Z","uid":1806,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3c26ff9904cf054986111fb6bac57ffaf9e7dd87","tid":1816494,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前我哋可愛系設計師合作，出咗4款鼠年賀年Postcard卡同揮春嘅設計，俾大家print嚟派街坊或寫俾手足之後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><blockquote>文宣注入節日行動 2.0 - 光復農曆新年Postcard + 賀年光復揮春正式上線啦！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1812241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1812241</a></blockquote></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今次輸到分析派立體主義風格作品既設計師出場，繼續一反傳統風格，將神獸獅鳥同靜雞雞嘅力量注入揮春，實行文藝救港！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QrNMGqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQrNMGqO.jpg&h=9a9f7cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家公開俾各位巴打絲打下載使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">印刷用的PDF檔</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>Download: <a href=\"https://cdn.hkgetv.com/file/2020_lunarnewyear/faichun_art_1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hkgetv.com%2Ffile%2F2020_lunarnewyear%2Ffaichun_art_1.pdf&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=9d1b15cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hkgetv.com/file/2020_lunarnewyear/faichun_art_1.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Printer 用的PDF檔</span></strong><br />\n<blockquote>Download: <a href=\"https://cdn.hkgetv.com/file/2020_lunarnewyear/faichun_art_2.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hkgetv.com%2Ffile%2F2020_lunarnewyear%2Ffaichun_art_2.pdf&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=1e72c50c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hkgetv.com/file/2020_lunarnewyear/faichun_art_2.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">此為非賣品<br />\n作品只供市民印刷並作免費派發之用，嚴禁將以上作品用作任何商業用途。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">HKGETV Social Media Platform<br />\n<strong><blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatured&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=96711511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured</a><br />\nOur Facebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=4abe2aa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=45eb6385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkgetv&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=6b0ab6ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkgetv</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Telegram Channel (New!):</span><a href=\"https://t.me/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkgetv&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=79872cd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkgetv</a></blockquote></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e574e207fb12451bdb6bba271cfa6597fba907